	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Accepi binas literas simul, dedi tertias d. <persName ref="p714">Caelio</persName>, qui dixit nihil se habere, quod rescribat; si quid novi ex <placeName ref="l834">Italia</placeName> habuerit, tecum velle brevi communicare.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Ago etiam gratias tibi propter nova illa, quę et nos habuimus; sed tu clariora scribis et quędam addis, quę nobis non sunt scripta.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Expectamus in singulas horas literas ex <placeName ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Communicavi <persName ref="p2916">Schertlin</persName> et <persName>baron Georgio</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la"><persName>Caesar</persName> nuper audivit missam, puto in festo trium regum, et quum pfaffus praelegeret evangelium de <persName>Herode</persName>, corruit ipse in sacello Fuggeranorum; accursum est a ministris, et pfaffus reliquit in hoc tumultu altare ad Caesarem currens ac clamans: "Domine Caesar, invoca Iesum salvatorem."</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Sublevatus est et reportatus ad conclave suum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Mox iussus accersiri ad se sororem <persName>Mariam</persName>, quę tunc erat <placeName ref="l513">Ulmę</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Putant quidam illum tactum ab angelo dei quemadmodum <persName ref="p18508">Herodes</persName> in Actis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Dominus illius misereatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Pulchre me irrides, quod parvum donulum miserim et maximum receperimus.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Fortunatus sum mercator, si ita perrexero mercari; brevi plura lucrari potero, quam <persName>Fuggerani</persName> habent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Sed hęc ioco.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la">Brevi plura.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la">A domino quęstore plura percipies.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la">19. ianuarii 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278">Gastius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de">An den wolgelerten herren <persName ref="p495">Heinrych Bullinger</persName>, prędicanten zuͦ <placeName ref="l587">Zurich</placeName> im münster, mynem günstigen herren, zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de"><placeName ref="l587">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
